<p>The <a href="https://shadowd.zecure.org">Shadow Daemon</a> server received an invalid message authentication code from the connector.</p>
<p>The key of the <a href="https://shadowd.zecure.org/documentation/user_interface/">profile</a> and the key of the <a href="https://shadowd.zecure.org/documentation/connectors/">connector</a> do not match. One or both of them have to be corrected.</p>
